      "file_path": "main/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/pdpx/main/XacmlState.java",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 110,
      "message": "For what I see this object is created at initialization, see XacmlPdpActivator.java, I don't think there is any place where it is unset, you can assume that this will be set.   In any case, if null, you can simply log an error and return, I tend to think that is better not to try to recreate a new object.",
