      "file_path": "main/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/pdpx/main/XacmlState.java",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 121,
      "message": "I don't think we know this at this point, track the code for PDP_UPDATE for deploy/undeploy to properly track this count. The Permit decissions count will correspond more to PdpStatistics.policyExecutedSuccessCount  instead of the deploy success count.",
